      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Version 0.3.8\r\n\r\n**Bug Fixes**\r\n\r\n- #92 __Hopefully__ fixed stale cursor positions when applying suggestions\r\n- #120 Fixed tooltip showing during text selection\r\n- #130 Fixed jump-to-next/previous suggestion navigation and added auto-scroll to selected suggestions\r\n\r\n**Features**\r\n\r\n- Added CommonMark-compliant inline code validator (PR #142 by @NickPisp)\r\n\r\n**Technical Changes**\r\n\r\n- Updated esbuild to 0.25.5 and TypeScript to 5.8.3\r\n- Removed legacy CodeMirror 5 support files\r\n- Updated CI/CD to Node.js 20\r\n\r\nPlease provide feedback in the related issues if this was fixed for you, especially for #92. As the bug is fairly random and hard to replicate, I can't fully verify if the fix worked.",
